title: Game Of Thrones Logon Screen
description:
Download and Enjoy Game Of Thrones Logon Screen


An epic story that blend the darkest passions of desire, power, ambition. A novel that has become a mass phenomenon, faithfully carried television. Game Of Thrones Logon Screen contain 5 high quality backgrounds to replace the default Windows Logon Wallpaper. The winter is coming!.



Sequential Mode: Incremental rotation of 5 logon wallpapers on every restart.
Random Mode: Randomize the logon wallpapers on every restart.
User choice: Choose the desire logon wallpaper from the preview list and use only this.





==================================================================

OS: Windows 8, 7, Vista, 2003, XP, 2000, 98, Me, NT

Howto Install Screensavers/Animated Wallpapers On Windows Vista / 7 / 8
Right-click in the program installer, and then click Run As Administrator

Enjoy!
